data.description: Lovely, well-maintained home in East Pennsboro School District.  Gorgeous hardwood flooring throughout the first and second floors. Cozy family room off the kitchen includes a fireplace and sliding glass doors to the rear deck and patio.  Kitchen includes granite countertops and hardwood flooring.  Lots of room to play in the level back yard.  Partially finished basement includes a nice sized rec room and another room currently used as a 4th bedroom.  Situated in Pine Ridge Estates on a street which leads to a cul-de-sac, the backyard backs up to the grounds of East Pennsboro Elementary School.  Conveniently located to all levels of East Pennsboro Schools and other amenities.  Move-in Ready for it's next owner.
